				<p>Hi KJ — I’ve got a ton of <a href="http://smittenkitchen.com/2009/03/layer-cake-tips-the-biggest-birthday-cake-yet/" rel="nofollow">layer cake tips here</a> that I hope will help. Briefly, I’ve got a small freezer and they did fit. I would freeze the layers <i>or</i>
 keep them at room temperature but not make them more than a day or two 
